      <prop type="x-translation-ref">行露.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>厭浥行露，豈不夙夜，謂行多露。
誰謂雀無角？何以穿我屋？誰謂女無家？何以速我獄？雖速我獄，室家不足。
誰謂鼠無牙？何以穿我墉？誰謂女無家？何以速我訟？雖速我訟，亦不女從。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>y DU y vul ym
Who can say that you did not get me betrothed?
How else could you have urged on this trial?
But though you have forced me to trial,
I will still not follow you.</seg>
      </tuv>
